latestPosts.caption:
Monsoon madness served hot—with pakoras, Maggi, banana chips & maa ke haathon ki kulhad chai. Rain, UNO, and a balcony view to seal the vibe. 🌧️🫖🃏 #achanceofchai #ChaiAndChaos

The skies broke into a soft drizzle, and just like clockwork, our kitchen turned into a snack haven. Mom whipped up a sizzling batch of pakoras, someone passed around banana chips (because what’s a monsoon without them?), and the comforting aroma of Maggi mingled with the scent of wet earth. We gathered on the balcony—my whole fam jam, a hot cup of chai in one hand, UNO cards in the other. Laughter bounced off the walls with every +4 drama, and someone always tried to bend the rules. The rain played backup music while our snacks stole the show. It wasn’t just food—it was madness, memories, and monsoon magic, all rolled into one cozy, crunchy moment. 🌧️✨🃏🍴

#monsoon #rain #rainyseason
